menu "breadboard: bb_mqtt_info"

config BB_MQTT_INFO_AUTOREGISTER
    bool "Auto-register /api/health \"mqtt\" section via bb_init"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, bb_mqtt_info self-registers the "mqtt" health section
        through bb_init (regular tier, order 1). Consumers that call
        bb_mqtt_register_health() manually must leave this disabled; enabling
        both double-registers the section. Default n preserves backward-
        compatible manual-register behavior.

        To switch to auto-register: enable this option and remove the
        bb_mqtt_register_health() call from app_main / bringup code.

endmenu
